text:
Thanks for your hard work today.
Thanks to Amana's hard work, we got good results.
Hehe, it's all thanks to everyone's help.

Of course, Producer-san too!
Thanks as always.

But I have to go home now.
It's a bit sad to think this is our last walk.

We walked here every day.
Thanks to that, I've gotten to know this area pretty well.

We found lots of back alleys and stuff.
I've become quite familiar with them.

Haha...
Let's come again together sometime.

If there's a chance to come for work,
let's explore together.
